itunes:title: WHO CARES ABOUT COLLEGE?!? BACK to SCHOOL... or NOT? | EP 44
title: WHO CARES ABOUT COLLEGE?!? BACK to SCHOOL... or NOT? | EP 44
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description:
Did you go to college? Are you proud or regretful?

Is college right for everyone? How WE figured out if college was the right choice for us (or our kids). So many kids these days simply go to college after high school because “that’s what you're

supposed to do”…. right?!!

But we are here today chatting about breaking that cycle of what’s considered “normal”.


Let us know if you went to college and are actually using your degree, or if you didn’t go then what are you up to now?!

We are also on Spotify, Apple Podcast and more! Search "Yeah No I Know".

* Everything we talk about on this podcast is our own individual opinions, not fact. Research everything for yourself and make the best decisions for you.
